Reasoning: The paper focuses on developing a sensor suite for mobile robotics applications, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The sensor suite involves multiple cameras and visual-inertial fusion, which suggests computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) may also be relevant sub-categories. The paper also discusses time synchronization and host clock translation, which could fall under systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper demonstrates the versatility of the sensor suite in multiple applications, including mapping and reconstruction, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
